    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run a Café is a game where you do just that, run a Café! Start from a bare bones Café and become the most successful coffee shop! Be sure you keep your customers happy and your store well stocked! Unhappy customers means less sales, and less sales means game over! Keep the highest ratings for the most business and sore to the top of the chain as a dominant player in the coffee business! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make drinks from regular coffee, to iced flavored coffees and even serve food!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372250/extras/35d16e4337cdbe39d9ce1a4c50811e9a.avif?t=1744139346\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372250/extras_big/35d16e4337cdbe39d9ce1a4c50811e9a.avif?t=1744139346 width=800 height=434 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ensure every customer gets their order!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372250/extras/2a10c5baef82389f656ab755c5da9cc2.poster.avif?t=1744139346\" width=608 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372250/extras/2a10c5baef82389f656ab755c5da9cc2.webm?t=1744139346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372250/extras/2a10c5baef82389f656ab755c5da9cc2.mp4?t=1744139346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Watch your money to make sure you always have enough  for the daily rent!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/237225